Advances in Space Research 31(8), 1883-1888, 2003
(doi: 10.1016/S0273--1177(03)00162-5)


EIGEN-2 is a CHAMP-only gravity field model derived from CHAMP
GPS satellite-to-satellite and accelerometer data out of the
period 2000, July to December, and 2001, September to December.

http://op.gfz-potsdam.de/champ/results/index_RESULTS.html



